{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_51_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 調子が狂う誕生日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、なんで私まで料理を作ることに\nなってるんでしょう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ why am I the one making\nthe food…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 7.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依がこの調子だから、貴方に任せるしかないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Rui like this‚ I have no choice but to leave it to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やっぱり美味しい。具材をグミに変えて\n正解だったわね。この食感と弾力、絶品だわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ it's delicious. Replacing the ingredients\nwith gummy candy was the right choice. This texture and elasticity are exquisite!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……怜には期待してるわよ\n確か、手作りのお弁当を作っていたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m counting on you‚ Rei.\nYou used to make your own bento‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7383518917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.7666688283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありましたっけ……？\nというか、なんで料理が上手だって思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I……?\nMore importantly‚ why do you think I’m good at cooking……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7471865733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.433335495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "『もしも君と恋をしたら』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"If We Fell in Love.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.433335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.8666688283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "はいっっ！？　えっ！？　あのっ、もしかして\n私が出た恋愛ゲームの話をしてます！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? What!? Wait‚ are you\ntalking about that romance game I was in!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "あのゲームのヒロインは貴方、一ノ瀬怜でしょう\nブリのおかずを沢山作っていたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The heroine of that game is you‚ Ichinose Rei.\nYou made a lot of yellowtail dishes‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.2666688283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私も、そのシーン見ました\n怜が本気で作った料理、私も食べてみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw that scene too.\nI’d like to try some food that Rei-san made with all her heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.6000021617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あれは理想を……というか、プレイしてたんですね……\nはぁ、分かりました。そこまで言うなら頑張ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was just an ideal… I mean‚ you actually played it…\nSigh‚ fine. I’ll give it a shot since you’re insisting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 74
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "余ってたご飯を……んしょ……お塩もつけて……\nあら？　多かったかしら……でも、うん、平気よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taking the leftover rice… Heave ho… Add some salt…\nHuh? Did I add too much…? Well‚ it should be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.6333360036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "出来ました。一ノ瀬怜特製、塩むすびです！\nちょっとだけ、お塩が多かったかもしれませんが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here it is. Ichinose Rei’s special salted rice balls!\nI might have added a little too much salt‚ but――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.663996400004,
          "startTime": 97.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.8000001272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、{user}さんですか？\nまた生ゴミ……料理を作り過ぎてしまいまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san?\nWe have some more garbage… I made too much food…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3982247075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 105.4000001272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "って食べる前から電話しないで下さいっ！？\nおにぎりは前にも作ったし、失敗はしてないはず――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t call him before you’ve even tried it!?\nI’ve made rice balls before‚ and I haven’t failed――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 113.5666662853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "あむ……。う……しょっぱい……！\nなんで？　こんなにしょっぱいはずは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chomp… Ugh… It’s salty…！\nWhy? It shouldn’t be this salty…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6460215797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 122.5999996186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "塩はメーカーによって味が違うのよ\nゲームの中の一ノ瀬怜は、随分と設定を盛ったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Salt tastes different depending on the brand.\nThe Ichinose Rei in the game embellished her profile quite a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 131.0666662853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……だ、だって憧れるじゃないですか。誰かに\nご飯を作って、「美味しい」って言ってもらえるのって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Ugh… But it’s something to aspire to‚ isn’t it?\nTo make food for someone and have them say “It’s delicious?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 140.6999996186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……『美味しい』。バラエティとしては",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…”Delicious.” As entertainment‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 145.9666662853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "全然褒められてる気がしません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn’t feel like a compliment at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 149.2666662853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あら、私はこのおにぎり、普通に美味しいと思うわよ？\n中にグミを混ぜるとさらに美味しいわ。特にコーラ味",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I actually think these rice balls are pretty good?\nIt would be even more delicious if you mixed some gummy candy in. Especially cola flavor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 159.1333329519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それもあんまり嬉しくないんだけど……\nもしかして、瑠依って味音痴なのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That doesn’t make me happy either……\nAre you a terrible cook‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 167.0333329519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしなくてもそうでしょう\n……当日は、私一人で料理することになりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You definitely are.\n…Looks like I’ll be cooking by myself that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 174.2333329519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "お力になれず、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry I couldn't be of help…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2333329519,
